{"tid":1403953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買物資注意 琴晚夢遊發現前線裝備精良 係差個氣密護目鏡","createTime":"2019-08-04T01:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:01:32.000Z","uid":105976,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eba1129a6a21df1ba3a5ca28d708a3b9a9608e88","tid":1403953,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:23:47.000Z","msg":"琴晚發夢幫前線升級    發現好多人都裝備精良 有手腳護墊/甲  有D仲身體護甲<br />\n豬嘴全set  有6092X既人佔一半以上  (雖然仲有部份人直接6006, 事後表示頂唔順) <br />\n夢見一堆6200係冇人拎  (中後排好多都齊裝, 大後方就只綠罩)<br />\n<br />\n個個精神高昂   係差一副氣密護目鏡  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用泳鏡都係少量 明明有好多人眼鏡唔係必需 (剩係近視)  但都係眼鏡+漏氣既護目鏡<br />\n然後事後就話對眼好那  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雪鏡既feelback係條邊位海棉會有少少漏氣 <br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家加強下對眼既防護 用返泳鏡     要戴眼鏡既搵返副otg氣密鏡 (我知好多人訂左大量, 但仲未運到)<br />\n<br />\n武運昌隆<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全防具詳解&amp;購買連結  更新左日系氣密護目鏡  強烈建議睇   用PC開</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=117e1b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"0641a06425417041cc7c9cb34916b916778d0499","tid":1403953,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"改裝非氣密有冇用？"},{"pid":"f3b4ed4b8f0d7b31bba491df049925135c9cd2ca","tid":1403953,"uid":105976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmipSar.jpg\" data-th